{"tid":1592971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬鞍山富寶花園男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-09-25T00:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T05:13:08.000Z","uid":22095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bdc607a0923991b721f2c2381ce9fecfd0c618e5","tid":1592971,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山錦英路6號富寶花園，今日(25日)清晨5時50分，一名40餘歲男子由上址一大廈墮樓，保安員發現報警，惟經救護員檢驗，證實事主已返魂乏術。警員經調查後，相信事件無可疑，並召黑箱車將遺體舁送殮房。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=a3514c6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190925/mobile/bkn-20190925061736543-0925_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190925%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190925061736543-0925_00822_001.html&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUsF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=29f7bf50\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190925/mobile/bkn-20190925061736543-0925_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又嚟多單 白粉報依舊獨家拎料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fb5945585718e17fb3578edf10422de1a24541","tid":1592971,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-l